name: Zipcode
description: 5 digit Zipcode or military postal code(FPO/APO)

name: ZipCodeType
column4: PO BOX Only, Unique, Military(implies APO or FPO)

name: State
description: USPS offical state, territory, or quasi-state (AA, AE, AP) abbreviation code

name: Location
description: Standard Display  (eg Phoenix, AZ ; Pago Pago, AS ; Melbourne, AU )

name: Decommisioned
description: If Primary location, Yes implies historical Zipcode, No Implies current Zipcode; If not Primary, Yes implies Historical Placename

name: TaxReturnsFiled
description: Number of Individual Tax Returns Filed in 2008

name: EstimatedPopulation
description: Tax returns filed + Married filing jointly + Dependents

name: TotalWages
description: Total of Wages Salaries and Tips
